        "text_hrxC8n": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Appreciate your interest in Ludic.</p>\n<p>\n  Let's cut to the chase—it's not a tear-jerker, and we're not trying to be.<br>\n  But we think you'll enjoy getting to know us.\n</p>\n<p>\nHere's the bottom line: Ludic is a footwear-first lifestyle brand. We envisioned Ludic as a footwear brand from the start, but it naturally grew into something bigger.\n</p>\n<p> \nLet's break it down: why should fashion follow a one-size-fits-all\nmodel? This isn't a novel idea, but it's a problem worth solving. Creating something distinct that resonates with everyone? Not an easy task, but that's\nwhere we knew we could make an impact. We weren't here to overhaul the entire\nfashion industry, but we were ready to close the gap where it counted.</p>\n<p><i>That's how Ludic came to life.</i></p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0885/3834/9878/files/1_About_Ludic.png?v=1732535192\" style=\"display:none\">\n<p>Sure, the fashion market is saturated—we won't pretend otherwise. But if you look close enough, you'll see where there's room to innovate. For us, that was a glaring gap: India didn't have a brand that truly understood in Indian style, fit, and culture. It's no wonder international brands were taking the lead. So we decided to build something different—something that fit the Indian consumer from the inside out. Thoughtfully crafted, homegrown, and completely original.</p>\n<p>Every piece we produce is designed with intention. We look globally for inspiration, but it's all tailored for India. No shortcuts, no mass-market compromises. We're talking about high-quality, comfortable products with that extra touch that feels uniquely you.</p><p>\n</p><p>When the brand foundation was set, we turned our attention to the\nnarrative. Ludic wasn't going to be another athletic wear brand, and it wasn't\ngoing to be all about chasing the next fashion craze. We found a middle ground—a\nunique space that balanced both.</p>\n<p>Ludic is made for movement, built for a lifestyle that's always in motion. It's practical without sacrificing personality, reliable without being predictable. This isn't just something you put on; it's something that becomes part of your story.</p>\n\n<p>And because storytelling is at our core, every detail of Ludic has meaning.<br> Every product, every interaction—it all has a story behind it.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
